      "writtenOn": "2026-06-10T13:10:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Done in PS22 with a narrower predicate than suggested: pt is protocol-guaranteed for call wakeups (the daemon always labels call connection requests audioCall/videoCall — jamiaccount.cpp), and unconditional reconnect on PRIORITY_HIGH would reintroduce the full DHT/SIP reconnect on every message push that an earlier review round removed (DHT values default to high priority). PS22 treats a high-priority push with pt entirely absent as call-like (defensive against a proxy failing to copy the type), while explicit non-call pt values (sip, git…) keep the message path.",
